<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-09-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-09-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="599" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d599">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">
                                <gloss target="#t_JCS1">J.C.S.</gloss> Files: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Commander in Chief, Allied Force
                                    Headquarters</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Eisenhower</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Combined Chiefs of Staff</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                    <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">urgent</hi>
                                </seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Algiers</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-09-01">1 September
                                        1943</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <gloss target="#t_W1">W</gloss>–8899/9175. Signal from General
                                    C<note n="1" xml:id="d599fn1">Giuseppe Castellano.</note> states
                                that reply is in affirmative (To <gloss target="#t_AGWar1">AGWar</gloss> for Combined Chiefs of Staff and to <gloss target="#t_USFor1">USFor</gloss> for British Chiefs of Staff
                                signed Eisenhower cite <gloss target="#t_fhdsc1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">fhdsc</hi></gloss>. This is <gloss target="#t_Naf1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Naf</hi>
                                </gloss> 348) and that he will arrive at the appointed meeting place
                                tomorrow September 2.</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>